t a waiver to enforce our rights at any time for the same or different offenses.</p><h2>DESCRIPTION OF SERVICES AND PRODUCTS</h2><p>VREF and its Website, <a href=\u0022//www.VREF.com\u0022>www.VREF.com</a>, provides access to a variety of resources and Content, including but not limited to <strong>VREF Aircraft Value Reference®, VREF Online®, VREF Verified Reports, VREF Appraisals, and VREF published books</strong>, historical value data, modifications, interval and schedule for maintenance, resale pricing trends, residual values, market data, marketing and communication updates, and product and service information (collectively \u0022Services and Products\u0022). The Services and Products, including any updates, revisions, enhancements, new features, and the addition of any new material, concepts, and/or design concepts and materials, are subject to the T&amp;C.</p><h2>AUTHORIZED USERS</h2><p>Authorized Users refer to subscription account holders. In order to access VREF subscription content, you must be an Authorized User. Authorized Users are subscribers that have paid in full, agreed to VREF Terms of Use, completed the vetting process, and are in compliance with the T&amp;C.</p><p>VREF reserves the right to deny access to the Website at <a href=\u0022//www.VREF.com\u0022>www.VREF.com</a>, and any subscription-based tool, features, and data, for any user that is deemed to be misusing the information provided through our subscriptions or information that is made available on the public areas of the Website, or any other VREF publications.</p><h2>SUBSCRIPTIONS</h2><p>Only Authorized Users are permitted access to the <a href=\u0022//www.VREF.com\u0022>www.VREF.com</a> subscription-based content, tools, features, and data.</p><p>Once you have placed an order for a subscription, the subscription will continue unless it is ended by the subscription expiration date, canceled by you, or canceled or suspended by us in accordance with the T.O.U. Please note that there are 